snippet.title: Beep Bap The Beep Boop Demo - Sage Teaser & Release!
snippet.description:
Beep Bap The Beep Boop is a 3D platformer inspired by Spyro, Banjo and Zelda!
Explore colorful worlds and talk to a variety of charming NPCs!
Use your surroundings to aid in combat & use shields to block and parry enemy attacks!

https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/beep-bap-the-beep-boop-sage-23-demo.1766/

This is a game me and LukeStation made, I hope you enjoy!
Join our socials down here and let us know what you think!
